CustomField.description: N — Not confirmed; address is not present in the USPS data. S — Confirmed by ignoring secondary info; the main address is present in the USPS data, but the submitted secondary information (apartment, suite, etc.) was not recognized. (e.g., 62 Ea Darden Dr Apt 298 Anniston, AL) D — Confirmed but missing secondary info; the main address is present in the USPS data, but it is missing secondary information (apartment, suite, etc.). (e.g., 122 Mast Rd Lee, NH) [blank or null] — The address is not present in the USPS database.
